      "raw_text": "One man is believed to have been killed and Is injured\nin headon collision between two through Spokane Port\nland Seattle passenger trains the Seventh\ntrese of the Northern Pacific at 9:30 o'clock last night\n\n\nThat there not more fatalities appears almost\nmiraculous as the two trains came together with terrific\nforce on the trestle, fifty feet above the ground\n\n\nThe most seriously injured construction laborers\ncaught in the forward end of the smoker the easbound\ntrain, which was telescoped by the express"
